      <title>交易员权衡利比亚和沙特增加供应的可能性，油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 成员国沙特阿拉伯和利比亚有望增加供应，油价在连续两天大幅下跌之后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据巩固降息预期，美国国债价格上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新经济数据增强了美联储进一步降息的预期，美国国债价格上涨。一项指标凸显了对美国经济的乐观情绪，股市波动不定，一度上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 22:40:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>开普勒的 Barrett 谈对冲基金市场、中东、伦敦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/kepler-s-barrett-on-hedge-fund-market-mideast-london-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Kepler Partners 管理研究主管 Matthew Barrett 表示，在高利率环境下，基金经理正在考虑高波动性策略和多元化。在 Kepler 在伦敦温布利球场举办 Absolute Hedge Liquid Alternatives 峰会期间，Barrett 接受了彭博社 Dani Burger 的独家采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/kepler-s-barrett-on-hedge-fund-market-mideast-london-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:52:47 GMT</pubDate>
